VPC Traffic Mirroring
Allows you to cpature and inspect n/w traffic in your VPC
Route the traffic to security appliances that you manage
Capture the traffic
From (source) - ENIs
To (Targets) - an ENI or a N/w Load Balancer
Cpature all packets or capture the packets of you interest(optionally, trnacte packets)
Source and target can be in the same VPC or different VPCs(VPC Peering)
